			<h3>How Does Streamlyne Predict and Prevent downtime</h3>

			<br/>
			<p>We take all the raw, unstructured, user generated data from three separate silos:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Asset Management Systems (IBM, SAP, Oracle, OpenText); </li>
				<li>Distributed Control Systems (Invensys, Honeywell, Siemens)</li> 
				<li>Operator user generated information/input</li>
			</ul>
			<p>We then take this complex data and run it through Streamlyne’s Custom Analytics Platform and generate simple and user-friendly graphic images that display new trends and analytics for operators and managers.
			</p>

			<br/>
			<h4>VP’s and Manager  Capabilities</h4>
			<p>Now VP’s and managers can view all system and user generated information - for one or multi-site plants.</p>

			<br/>
			<h4>Operator Capabilities</h4>
			<p>Operators now have a user-friendly iOS mobile application so they can view and input real-time asset information right at their fingertips.
			</p>

